E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1347','6','郑晟','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span>日，我县召开水利普查汇总平衡工作会。县水利普查办公室全体成员、各镇分管领导和普查指导员参加会议。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">会上，县水利普查办公室技术总负责人蔡柏树分别就水利工程、经济社会用水、河湖开发治理保护、行业能力建设、灌区、地下水取水井等六个专项的普查数据汇总平衡以及综合数据汇总平衡流程、方法和要求进行了详细讲解。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">会议要求，各镇要增强水利普查工作的责任感和紧迫感。市里要求<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>日前完成普查表填表工作，各镇分管同志要进一步加强组织领导，做到队伍不散、劲头不减，尽快完成普查底表数据补充完善，台账建设规范，普查表正式填表，普查数据上机录入，以及普查数据汇总平衡等工作。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 会议强调，全县各级水利普查机构要严格按照省市县普查办&ldquo;一条主线、两个阶段、三大任务、四个节点&rdquo;的总体安排，进一步强化普查质量控制，切实抓住普查数据填报、审核、汇总、平衡等关键环节，严把数据检查审核关，确保普查成果经得起实践和历史。</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1348','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-25/1c01a56194fb6d5da78fc76a31da1ceb.jpg\\\\\" alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">测评会现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">24</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，市直机关工委组织社会评议测评小组赴我县，对</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">113</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家市直目标责任制单位进行满意度测评。市直机关工委副书记张兴宏，县领导李国光、熊武华、雷家兴出席测评会。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，到场参加社会评议的代表有县级领导，县直责任单位的负责人和班子成员代表，还有县党代表、人大代表、政协委员代表及民主党派人士代表、企业代表等。他们对市直</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">113</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">家责任单位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度的工作目标责任完成情况进行现场评议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光要求参加测评的代表要以高度的政治责任感，认真阅读、准确把握测评表的各项内容，本着对组织负责、对目标责任制单位负责的态度，严肃认真、实事求是地对各个市直单位作出客观公正的评价。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm;\\\\\" class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1349','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日，记者从县委办获悉，近期我县将开展&ldquo;学雷锋、讲文明、树新风&rdquo;主题实践月活动，旨在通过各种形式的实践活动，弘扬雷锋精神，不断提升公民道德素质和社会文明程度。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，从<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日开始，全县各镇、县直各单位将采取悬挂横幅、张贴标语、出墙报等形式，大力宣传雷锋精神。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在实践月期间，我县将组织动员社会各界志愿者深入社区、养老院等，开展&ldquo;学习雷锋、奉献爱心&rdquo;社会志愿服务活动；组织县直各单位工作人员深入各自责任路段开展&ldquo;清洁家园、美化环境&rdquo;活动；在各校开展学雷锋演讲、文艺演出、读书征文等活动；在各企业开展&ldquo;岗位学雷锋、争做好员工&rdquo;活动等。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县委办要求，各单位在此次主题实践活动中，要通过媒体营造良好氛围，扩大学雷锋活动的覆盖面和影响力。同时注重群众参与，增强活动的实际效果，让雷锋精神深入人心，使学雷锋活动深入千家万户。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1350','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-02-27/683d525dfc824971d44de5bf2023e4b9.jpg\\\\\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇出席会议并讲话</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日，全省党的基层组织建设工作电视电话会议召开，就全省开展&ldquo;基层组织建设年&rdquo;、双联双促和五亮五比五创等三项活动进行动员部署。县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，县委常委、组织部长袁秋明，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权，县委办主任章斌在嘉鱼分会场出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全省电视电话会指出，基层组织建设工作重点要抓好基层组织带头人，发挥组织书记的主心骨和领头雁作用；要结合治庸问责、创先争优活动，着力破解基层组织建设中的重点、难点问题；要整合各种资金，建立健全的人力、物力保障机制。加强基层组织建设工作要抓住支部，结合党员，通过开展五比五创等活动，调动广大党员树先进、学先进的积极性，多办一些贴近基层，顺应群众期盼的实事，真正实现强化党务、规范村（居）务、优化服务、拓展商务、协调事务的&ldquo;五务合一&rdquo;目标，真正把&ldquo;基层组织建设年&rdquo;工程办成群众的满意工程。抓基层组织建设，关键在党委，关键在书记，要坚持书记抓、抓书记，将党建工作放在重要位置，努力形成工作合力，严格考核制度，做到述职述党建、评议评党建、考核考党建、任用干部看党建。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">全省电视电话会后，县委书记熊征宇就贯彻会议精神作了强调。他指出，做好党的基层组织建设工作，要做到&ldquo;一把手抓&rdquo;和&ldquo;抓一把手&rdquo;，要选优配强村级班子，选出让组织放心、让群众满意的基层&ldquo;一把手&rdquo;，同时进行有针对性地培训，增强他们的工作能力，更好地推进基层组织建设。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇强调，当前我县的基层组织建设工作要抓好&ldquo;五务合一&rdquo;的全覆盖，即抓好农村党员群众服务中心卫生室、综合服务社、农家书屋、文体活动场所等配套设施建设；同时要抓好工作经费的全覆盖，即保障基层党组织正常运行的工作经费。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">熊征宇要求，在基层组织建设工作上，要注重三个工作方法，一是要创新工作思路，抓典型，出亮点；二是要求真务实，结合自身实际，以推动村级集体经济发展壮大为目标，有针对性地开展基层组织建设工作；三是要严格抓督办，确保党的基层组织建设各项工作落到实处。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1351','6','曾祥惠、张兴旺、周志兵等','湖北日报','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">土地日益成为稀缺资源。有限国土，如何精耕、深耕？<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">14</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">日，我省<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>县市获全国国土资源节约集约模范县（市）称号，嘉鱼是全省唯一的土地、矿产兼有型模范县。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">21</span>日，记者赴该县踏访，所见所闻令人欣喜。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">向天要地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【现场】嘉鱼经济开发区，湖北中能锂电公司。梁仁俊，公司行政总监，与记者一道参观<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万平方米的三层厂房。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">一楼，电池涂布、配料、正负极整片车间；二楼，装配、注液、老化、包装，一排排插满电池成品的检测柜挤满了检测库。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>三楼目前空置，今年将上聚合物锂电项目。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>梁仁俊说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">公司计划投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>亿元，分四期完成。去年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月，首期投产。据介绍，公司本拟征地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>亩，听从国土部门建议后，设计多层厂房，节约用地三分之二。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【背景】建多层厂房，向天要地，只是嘉鱼节约用地的一招。该县还采取租赁、划转、收回等方式，盘活闲置土地资源。原嘉晟体育用品公司占地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">60</span>亩，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7000</span>平方米厂房一度只有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">15</span>名工人生产。经协商后，厂房租赁给金桦实业，县里不增一亩地，引进一家新企业；某游艇公司投资未达计划投资额的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">25%</span>，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>余亩土地闲置。县政府依法收回，以招拍挂形式重新出让。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【画外音】嘉鱼县委书记熊征宇：湖北是投资热土。短短几年，嘉鱼企业投资用地需求翻了几倍。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18</span>日，总投资<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">16</span>亿元的三木集团、汉方科技两项目开工建设，一批新项目还在排队。既要保护耕地，又要保增长，就必须精耕土地，提高土地利用率，为子孙后代留下发展空间。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">科学增地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【现场】武嘉公路旁，嘉鱼县潘家湾镇四邑村集中迁建居民点，建筑工人忙着房屋装修。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月，首批<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">103</span>户农民就要搬进来了。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">每栋房<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">219</span>平方米，农户只需交<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>万元即可入住，其余建设资金由土地整治资金、联乐集团分担。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>四邑村党支部书记周炳兰说，将有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">182</span>户农户迁居至此，只占地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">82</span>亩，可新增<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">450</span>亩耕地。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">两公里外的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>组农民游春明，现在住的房子是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>年前盖的，宅基地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.3</span>亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>新建<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>多平方米的房子，至少<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>万元以上，还没有迁建点那么好的配套设施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">搬家后，离家里种的菜地远了点。游春明说，关系不大，有手扶拖拉机呢。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【背景】嘉鱼是全省国土资源整治示范县之一。去年来，该县组织实施高产农田土地整理、低丘岗地改造、整村推进等项目<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>个，投入资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.5</span>亿余元，增加有效耕地面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9000</span>余亩。田野集团与有关部门整合资金，整治开发万亩油茶基地、千亩养殖基地，建设<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">800</span>户的官桥村居民新社区，将节约耕地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">870</span>亩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【画外音】嘉鱼县县长余珂：科学治理、科学调度，把不合格的土地整治好，把不该占的土地腾出来，可利用的土地资源就变多了。如此，用起土地，心里就不慌了。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">变废为宝<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【现场】<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>尾渣里也有宝啊。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>嘉鱼县蛇屋山金矿，站在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>米长、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>米宽的一处尾矿区旁，金矿公司副总经理陶长才告诉记者，公司去年利用新技术，综合利用低品位矿产，从尾矿中提炼出<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>公斤黄金。尾矿资源遍布矿区，如果全部选炼，可新增<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>吨产量。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">公司报表显示，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年开采回采率比<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年提高<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.1</span>个百分点，年增加效益<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>万元以上。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【背景】嘉鱼县推进矿山整合，由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2007</span>年的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">32</span>家减至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2010</span>年的<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>家。蛇屋山金矿，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2008</span>年由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>家小矿整合组建，每吨产量在全国同类矿中居领先，跻身全国黄金行业先进集体。马鞍山采石场因资源枯竭关闭后，废弃矿区重新治理开发，平整土地<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>亩，引进了锦业家具和嘉安混凝土两个项目。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">【画外音】嘉鱼县国土资源局局长吴鹏：在技改中增矿，在治理中找地。不可再生的矿产、土地资源，可以在集约中再利用。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1352','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，记者从嘉鱼县政府办了解到，该县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年政府工作报告中提出要着力办好的十件民生实事进展顺利，县政府将每季度对&ldquo;十件实事&rdquo;进展情况进行一次督办通报。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">全面实施新型农村基本养老保险，全年城镇新增就业岗位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5000</font></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个</span></b><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。年初我县举行&ldquo;春风送岗位&rdquo;企业用工招聘会，为返乡人员提供岗位</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2737</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">个，有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多人与用人单位达成就业意向。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24.1pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">解决</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万农村人口饮水问题，实施</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span></b><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万亩小型农田水利基础设施建设</span></b><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。目前前者已完成</span><span lang=\\