E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1365','79','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-05/29e3ef784357e8db9c1c4194e9e69203.jpg\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px\">座谈会现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>日<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>上海嘉麟杰公司董事长黄伟国一行就投资环境及项目选址事宜来我县参观考察。县长余珂、县委副书记李国光陪同考察。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">黄伟国一行先后来到嘉鱼县工业园区和鱼岳工业园区，详细了解园区独特的区位优势、合理的产业布局、优越的投资环境、便捷的交通体系以及全方位的配套优势。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">座谈会上，余珂向客人全面介绍了嘉鱼县人文历史、招商引资优惠政策和远景战略规划，尤其是四通八达的交通体系。他说，嘉鱼地属武汉城市圈，至武汉市区<span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span>公里，至天河机场<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>公里，至京珠高速公路入口和武广高速铁路<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>公里，武嘉一级路建成后，嘉鱼至武汉车程仅<span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span>分钟。长江黄金水道纵贯全境<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>公里，并有长江港口深水码头。武深高速和嘉鱼长江大桥建成后，嘉鱼对外交通将更加便捷。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">黄伟国表示，此次的考察参观，他们不仅看到了嘉鱼良好的自然条件、交通路网、战略地位和发展态势，更感到了嘉鱼县委县政府发展工业的决心和诚意，这进一步增强了他们在嘉鱼投资的兴趣。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">据了解，上海嘉麟杰公司是国家高新技术企业，公司成立于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span>年，注册资本<span lang=\"EN-US\">2.08</span>亿人民币，是<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>月深圳中小板上市公司，主要生产户外运动、高尔夫、休闲类编针织面料和服装，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年营业收入<span lang=\"EN-US\">7.2</span>亿元人民币。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1366','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">干净敞亮的诊断室、药房、观察室、治疗室等一应俱全，常见疾病预防知识、卫生药品价格表等全部上墙，新农合有关信息在公示栏里一目了然。这是</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，记者在潘家湾镇苍梧岭村卫生室看到的场景。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;以前有个头痛脑热的小病，要到几公里外的镇卫生院就医。现在村里有了卫生室，小病不出村就能治好，我们都很高兴。&rdquo;正带着孙子来看病的李婆婆告诉记者。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，为了缩小城乡医疗资源配置、服务利用和健康水平等方面的差距，让农村居民享有基本医疗卫生服务，我县从</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2005</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年开始，启动农村卫生室标准化改造工程。截至目前，全县已争取村级机构卫生场所建设项目资金</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多万元。对卫生所改造达到标准化建设要求的，给予补助</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元。改造后的村卫生所，有独立区分的诊断室、药房、观察室、治疗室，建筑面积基本达到</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"平方米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"120\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">120</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方米</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，医疗环境有了很大的改善。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">此外，为了提高村医医疗技术水平，该县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2005</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年开始实施村医免费培训工程，至今累计培训村医达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">800</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多人次，确保所有的乡村医生都培训到。据悉，村医培训课程贴近村医实际，学习内容包含了内科、外科、儿科的临床诊断治疗、临床护理、政策法规、计划免疫等相关知识。通过培训，提高村医对农村常见病、多发病的诊断与治疗能力，掌握常用药物的合理应用。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">目前，嘉鱼县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">以上的村级卫生室都达到了标准化建设标准，并力争在今年底通过&ldquo;整镇推进项目&rdquo;，让</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">100%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">的村级卫生室都达到标准化建设标准。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\" size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1367','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-05/254477c808e6df616d4e167b9d318312.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">义诊活动现场</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-05/846d5218329ca5936c9734ae93c8d8ea.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">走上街头参加清洁家园行动</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;学习雷锋好榜样，忠于革命忠于党。&rdquo;</span><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\" month=\\\\\"3\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">是&ldquo;学习雷锋日&rdquo;，记者从嘉鱼县文明办获悉，今天，全县各级各部门干部职工纷纷走上街头、进村入户开展清洁家园、文明劝导、免费义诊、慰问孤寡老人等活动，以实际行动践行&ldquo;学雷锋&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">上午</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，县国土局、高铁岭镇干部职工纷纷走上城区、镇区的大街小巷</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">,</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">拿着扫帚、抹布等清洁工具，清扫垃圾、疏通积水、清除牛皮癣，认真开展美化环境、清洁家园活动，赢得过往市民拍手称赞，许多市民还自觉加入清扫队伍，掀起了全民用实际行动向雷锋同志学习的热潮。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;请大家遵守交通规则，文明行车！&rdquo;&ldquo;请主动为老、弱、病、残让座！&rdquo;县交通局和团县委结合&ldquo;文明交通行动计划&rdquo;、&ldquo;文明让座日&rdquo;、&ldquo;出租车文明服务&rdquo;等活动，组织志愿者到城区主要路段、重要路口、公交站点向乘客和过往行人发放宣传资料，向市民弘扬传统美德，文明礼让，号召大家从我做起，从小事做起。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">中百购物广场门前，卫生局组织的&ldquo;学雷锋&rdquo;大型义诊的展台刚刚搭好，台前就排满了前来免费就医的市民。&ldquo;别担心，您这只是最近气温多变引起的感冒并发症。平时要注意健康饮食和按时作息，放松心态很快就好了！&rdquo;医护人员耐心的为前来求医问诊的群众答疑解惑。据了解，活动当天，共接待就诊群众</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人，受理健康咨询</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人，现场发放宣传资料</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余份。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&ldquo;在新时代，你们依然是最可爱的人，像是我们的亲孙子一样，非常亲切。&rdquo;上午<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9:30</span>，消防官兵们先后来到文庙山老年公寓、敬老院，帮忙疏通管道、打扫卫生、擦洗门窗、清理垃圾，陪孤寡老人们谈心拉家常，为老人们剪指甲、叠被子、讲故事，还不忘教给老人简单的防火、灭火和火场逃生技能，安全用火用电等常识，筑牢老人们的安全&ldquo;防火墙&rdquo;，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">将贴心服务和浓浓爱心送到了老人们的心坎上。</span><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，我县从本月起广泛开展&ldquo;学雷锋、讲文明、树新风&rdquo;主题实践月活动，旨在通过各种形式的实践活动，弘扬雷锋精神，引领社会风尚，不断提升全县人民道德素质和社会文明程度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">活动期间，我县将组织动员社会各界志愿者深入社区、养老院等，开展&ldquo;学习雷锋、奉献爱心&rdquo;社会志愿服务活动；组织县直各单位工作人员深入各自责任路段开展&ldquo;清洁家园、美化环境&rdquo;活动；在各校开展学雷锋演讲、文艺演出、读书征文等活动；在各企业开展&ldquo;岗位学雷锋、争做好员工&rdquo;活动等。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
