E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1369','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-03-06/45e6db6f2b100f98b7faf951e6a40563.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">查看农资销售台帐</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">正值春耕备耕时节，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">6</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，副县长魏萍率县农业、农机、工商、质监等部门负责人，对城区农资市场进行了全面检查，确保春耕生产顺利开展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为维护农资市场良好的经营秩序，确保农资安全，连日来，我县多措并举加大农资监管力度。县农业部门开办了种子法律法规培训班，对全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">120</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多家种子经营商进行培训，提高种子经营者的法律意识和识假能力。县工商部门对农资经营单位开展全面排查，对不具备经营资质的，停止其经营活动；对无照经营的，坚决予以取缔。县质监部门对农资商品进行抽样检测，清查掺杂使假、以次充好等制售假冒伪劣农资的坑农害农违法行为。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">检查中，魏萍详细了解了农资的价格及供应情况，并叮嘱经营户要严把质量关，依法经营；农业监管部门要负起责任，严厉打击和查处涉及农资的不法行为。切实维护好广大农民的合法权益。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
